      <title>git的使用</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/02/git/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/02/git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Git概述"><a href="#1-Git概述" class="headerlink" title="1 Git概述"></a>1 Git概述</h1><p>Git是一个免费的、开源的分布式版本控制系统（Distributed Version Control System，简称 DVCS），分为两种类型的仓库：本地仓库和远程仓库。</p><blockquote><p>a. 集中式版本控制工具<br>        集中式版本控制系统，版本库是集中存放在中央服务器，团队和个人工作时从中央服务器下载代码，必须联局域网或互联网才能工作，个人修改后再提交到中央版本库。</p><p>b. 分布式版本控制工具<br>        分布式版本控制系统没有中央服务器，每个人的电脑上都是一个完整的版本库，这样工作的时候，无需联网，多人协作时只需要将各自的修改推送给对方，就能互相看到对方的修改了。</p></blockquote><ul><li>git工作机制</li></ul><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221204223152446.png" alt="image-20221204223152446"></p><h1 id="2-Git的安装"><a href="#2-Git的安装" class="headerlink" title="2. Git的安装"></a>2. Git的安装</h1><p>Git官网：<a href="https://git-scm.com/download">https://git-scm.com/download</a></p><p>1) Git选项配置，默认选项，点击“Next”<br>   <img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205181813754.png" alt="image-20221205181813754"></p><ol><li><p>选择一个Vim编辑器，点击“Next”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205194659772.png" alt="image-20221205194659772"></p></li><li><p>是否修改初始化分支的名字，选择“Let Git decide”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205194900471.png" alt="image-20221205194900471"></p></li><li><p>是否修改环境变量，选择“Use Git from Git Bash only”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205195423645.png" alt="image-20221205195423645"></p></li><li><p>选择SSH可执行文件,勾选“use bundled OpenSSH”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205200122494.png" alt="image-20221205200122494"></p></li><li><p>勾选“Use the OpenSSL library”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205200913122.png" alt="image-20221205200913122"></p></li><li><p>勾选“Checkout Windows-style， commit Unix-style line endings”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205201555345.png" alt="image-20221205201555345"></p></li><li><p>勾选“Use MinITY (the default terminal of MsYs2)”<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205202043953.png" alt="image-20221205202043953"></p></li><li><p>选择默认的“git pull”行为<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205202523904.png" alt="image-20221205202523904"></p></li><li><p>选择凭据管理器<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205204511941.png" alt="image-20221205204511941"></p></li><li><p>其他配置<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205204817780.png" alt="image-20221205204817780"></p></li><li><p>配置实验室功能（不要勾选），点击“Install”，等待安装完成<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205205732076.png" alt="image-20221205205732076"></p></li><li><p>安装完成后，在桌面单击鼠标右键选择“Git Bash Here”。<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205210316210.png" alt="image-20221205210316210"></p></li><li><p>在弹出的对话框中，输入 <code>git --version</code> ,出现版本号，则表明安装成功<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205210643398.png" alt="image-20221205210643398"></p></li></ol><h1 id="3-GIt常用命令"><a href="#3-GIt常用命令" class="headerlink" title="3 GIt常用命令"></a>3 GIt常用命令</h1><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:left">命令名称</th><th>作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:left">git config —global user.name 用户名</td><td>设置用户签名</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git config —global user.email 邮箱</td><td>设置用户签名</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git init</td><td>初始化本地库</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git status</td><td>查看本地库状态</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git add 文件名</td><td>添加到暂存区</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git commit -m “日志信息” 文件名</td><td>提交到本地库</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git reflog</td><td>查看历史记录</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">git reset —hard 版本号</td><td>版本穿梭</td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 id="3-1-设置用户签名"><a href="#3-1-设置用户签名" class="headerlink" title="3.1 设置用户签名"></a>3.1 设置用户签名</h2><p>在“Git Bash Here”的对话框中输入以下指令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name 用户名</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email 邮箱</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>Git首次安装必须设置用户签名，其作用是区分不同操作者身份，否则后期无法提交代码。此处设置的用户签名和将来登录GitHub的账号无任关系。</p></blockquote><p>设置完成后，可以在<code>C:\Users\用户\.gitconfig</code> 文件中查看签名信息。</p><h2 id="3-2-初始化本地库"><a href="#3-2-初始化本地库" class="headerlink" title="3.2 初始化本地库"></a>3.2 初始化本地库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>当使用git管理某个目录时，需要让git获得该目录的管理权，即要在该目录下对本地库进行初始化。初始化后，会生成一个<code>.git</code>（隐藏）文件夹</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205215415513.png" alt="image-20221205215415513"></p><h2 id="3-3-查看本地库状态"><a href="#3-3-查看本地库状态" class="headerlink" title="3.3 查看本地库状态"></a>3.3 查看本地库状态</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首次运行时：<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205215915987.png" alt="image-20221205215915987"></p><p>新增文件后：<br><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205220444953.png" alt="image-20221205220444953"></p><h2 id="3-4-添加到暂存区"><a href="#3-4-添加到暂存区" class="headerlink" title="3.4 添加到暂存区"></a>3.4 添加到暂存区</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add 文件名 // 添加到暂存区</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git rm --cached 文件名  //将文件从暂存区删掉</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205221101970.png" alt="image-20221205221101970"></p><h2 id="3-5-提交到本地库"><a href="#3-5-提交到本地库" class="headerlink" title="3.5 提交到本地库"></a>3.5 提交到本地库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;日志信息&quot; 文件名  //提交到本地库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205222848572.png" alt="image-20221205222848572"> </p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>git reflog <span class="comment">//查看历史记录</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">log</span>  <span class="comment">//查看详细历史记录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205222905695.png" alt="image-20221205222905695"></p><h2 id="3-6-修改文件"><a href="#3-6-修改文件" class="headerlink" title="3.6 修改文件"></a>3.6 修改文件</h2><p>文件修改后需要重新添加到暂存区，提交到本地库</p><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205223748929.png" alt="image-20221205223748929"></p><h2 id="3-7-版本穿梭"><a href="#3-7-版本穿梭" class="headerlink" title="3.7 版本穿梭"></a>3.7 版本穿梭</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git reset --hard 版本号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picture-save-for-typora.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221205224552783.png" alt="image-20221205224552783"></p><blockquote><p>在<code>.\.git\HEAD</code>文件中查看当前分支（master）</p><p>在<code>.\.git\refs\heads\master</code>文件中查看当前指针所指向的版本</p><p>穿梭至哪个版本，则文件的内容也会回溯至该版本</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
